类 MesosArtifactServer

  • java.lang.Object

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    MesosArtifactResolver

    public class MesosArtifactServer
extends java.lang.Object
implements MesosArtifactResolver
    A generic Mesos artifact server, designed specifically for use by the Mesos Fetcher.

    More information: http://mesos.apache.org/documentation/latest/fetcher/ http://mesos.apache.org/documentation/latest/fetcher-cache-internals/
